<p><span>简直是难以置信，</span><span>液体真的瞬间凝固成了丝状，这也太神奇了吧！不过，这究竟是个啥原理呢？</span></p>
<p><span>被染色的液体是</span><span>海藻酸钠</span><span>，</span><span>而无色的液体是</span><span>乳酸钙</span><span>。</span><span>海藻酸钠中的</span><span>钠离子</span><span>，</span><span>被乳酸钙中的</span><span>钙离子</span><span>置换，</span><span>形成了</span><span>海藻酸钙凝胶</span><span>，</span>所以能快速成形。</p>
<p><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/q_70/images03/20201010/8417f100bb18452ea0d56d1f598077c5.jpeg" /></p>
<p><span><span>海藻酸钠</span></span><span>是</span><span>海藻</span><span>的提取物，</span><span>通常用在</span><span>食品行业</span><span>，</span><span>比如为</span><span>面食</span><span>增加</span><span>黏性</span><span>与</span><span>嚼劲</span><span>。</span><span>在</span><span>化妆品行业</span><span>中，</span><span>还可以作为制作</span><span>牙膏</span><span>与</span><span>洗发剂</span><span>等，</span><span><span>生活用品</span></span><span>的材料。</span></p>
